<h2>
    Shadow
</h2>
<p>
    The <code>text-shadow</code> property paints a shadow behind text. The horizontal and veritcal aspects 
    are defined, as well as the color and how blurry the shadow is. 
</p>
<pre><code class="lang-plain">
  text-shadow:
    horizontal vertical blur color; 

</code></pre>

